  <summary date="2021-08-10T19:39:24Z" status="Introduced in House">Children Don't Belong on Tobacco Farms Act

This bill prohibits as a form of oppressive child labor the employment of any employee under age 18 who has direct contact with tobacco plants or dried tobacco leaves.</summary>
